@ApiService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5471

### Get all tasks
GET {{ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/tasks
Accept: application/json

###

### Get task by ID (replace with actual ID from get all)
GET {{ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new task
POST {{ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Task from HTTP Client",
  "description": "This task was created using the HTTP client for testing",
  "status": 0,
  "dueDate": "2025-12-15T00:00:00Z"
}

###

### Update a task (replace ID)
PUT {{ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Task Title",
  "description": "This task has been updated with new information",
  "status": 1,
  "dueDate": "2025-12-20T00:00:00Z"
}

###

### Delete a task (replace ID)
DELETE {{ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

###
